                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12830965" author="srowen" created="Mon, 8 Feb 2010 15:11:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can take care of this in a bit. But one question, if it&apos;s Hadoop that needs CLI 1.1, and not us, shouldn&apos;t it get pulled in by Hadoop rather than require us to depend on it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12830970" author="drew.farris" created="Mon, 8 Feb 2010 15:22:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mahout doesn&apos;t pull commons-cli in directly, rather hadoop pulls it in as a transitive dependency. I had previously set an exclusion on the hadoop dependency for commons cli 1.1 which would prevent it from being pulled in because I did not think it was needed. Turns out it is. This patch removes that exclusion&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
